<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 12:21:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国首次承办戴维斯杯决赛小组赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/china-host-davis-cup-finals-group-stage-matches-first-time-2024-03-14/</link><description>国际网球联合会（ITF）周四表示，中国将于9月首次举办戴维斯杯决赛小组赛。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 12:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/china-host-davis-cup-finals-group-stage-matches-first-time-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于出口影响力引发摩擦，中国汽车制造商在海外开设工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-open-factories-abroad-export-clout-causes-friction-2024-03-14/</link><description>随着外国监管机构考虑对进口中国制造的电动汽车采取措施，寻求全球增长的中国汽车制造商正在海外市场建设更多汽车工厂。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-open-factories-abroad-export-clout-causes-friction-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>分析师表示，中国削减汽车首付的计划可能会落空</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-plan-cut-downpayments-cars-likely-fall-flat-analysts-say-2024-03-14/</link><description>分析师表示，中国通过削减汽车贷款首付来促进汽车销售的努力可能会因价格战和消费者谨慎而受挫，这主要有利于特斯拉和蔚来等少数受年轻买家青睐的品牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-plan-cut-downpayments-cars-likely-fall-flat-analysts-say-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特朗普发起中央情报局针对中国的秘密影响行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-launched-cia-covert-influence-operation-against-china-2024-03-14/</link><description>据直接了解这项高度机密行动的前美国官员透露，唐纳德·特朗普总统上任两年后，授权中央情报局在中国社交媒体上发起秘密活动，旨在扭转中国公众舆论反对中国政府。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-launched-cia-covert-influence-operation-against-china-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：石油玷污了通胀观点，特斯拉处于慢车道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-14/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国餐馆爆炸后媒体骚扰引发抗议和公众批评</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/media-harassment-after-china-restaurant-blast-sparks-protest-public-criticism-2024-03-14/</link><description>记者在试图报道北京郊外爆炸事件的后果时被当地居民和保安拦住，负责监管中国记者的协会发表了罕见的抗议声明。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 09:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/media-harassment-after-china-restaurant-blast-sparks-protest-public-criticism-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>意大利监管机构因内容检查对 TikTok 罚款 1100 万美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/italy-regulator-fines-tiktok-11-mln-over-inadequate-checks-harmful-content-2024-03-14/</link><description>意大利竞争监管机构周四表示，因对可能对年轻或弱势用户有害的内容检查不力，对社交媒体巨头 TikTok 的三个部门处以总计 1000 万欧元（1094 万美元）的罚款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 09:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/italy-regulator-fines-tiktok-11-mln-over-inadequate-checks-harmful-content-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>越南敦促中国在划定北部湾基线时尊重国际法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-urges-respect-international-law-china-draws-gulf-tonkin-baseline-2024-03-14/</link><description>越南外交部周四在回应有关中国本月早些时候划定北部湾基线的问题时表示，国际法和其他国家的权益必须得到尊重。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 09:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-urges-respect-international-law-china-draws-gulf-tonkin-baseline-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国周三发射DRO-A/B卫星未成功——官方媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-launch-dro-ab-satellite-wednesday-not-successful-state-media-2024-03-14/</link><description>据官方新华社周四报道，中国周三在西昌卫星发射中心发射的 DRO-A/B 卫星没有成功。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 08:33:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-launch-dro-ab-satellite-wednesday-not-successful-state-media-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部称美国提议的 TikTok 禁令“不公平”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/proposed-us-tiktok-ban-not-fair-chinas-foreign-ministry-says-2024-03-14/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周四表示，以国家安全为由削弱其他国家的竞争优势，“毫无公平可言”，并批评美国强制剥离或禁止 TikTok 的法案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 08:26:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/proposed-us-tiktok-ban-not-fair-chinas-foreign-ministry-says-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国腾讯收购字节跳动两个视频游戏团队 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-tencent-takes-over-two-bytedance-video-game-teams-source-2024-03-14/</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，在字节跳动去年退出游戏业务后，中国腾讯已经接管了字节跳动的两家视频游戏部门。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 08:16:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-tencent-takes-over-two-bytedance-video-game-teams-source-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>独家：由于全球供应过剩，中国买家取消、推迟澳大利亚小麦采购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-buyers-cancel-or-postpone-australian-wheat-buys-amid-global-oversupply-2024-03-14/</link><description>直接了解交易情况的贸易消息人士称，由于全球库存增加拖累价格，中国小麦进口商取消或推迟了约 100 万吨澳大利亚小麦货物。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 07:43:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-buyers-cancel-or-postpone-australian-wheat-buys-amid-global-oversupply-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯下周访问韩国并出席民主峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/blinken-visit-south-korea-next-week-attend-summit-democracy-2024-03-14/</link><description>首尔外交部周四表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯将于下周访问韩国，并于周一与国务卿赵泰烈举行会晤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 07:40:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/blinken-visit-south-korea-next-week-attend-summit-democracy-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>外交部称中国最高外交官将访问澳大利亚和新西兰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-top-diplomat-visit-australia-new-zealand-says-foreign-minsitry-2024-03-14/</link><description>周四，中国外交部长王毅在例行新闻发布会上表示，中国外交部长王毅将于3月17日至21日访问澳大利亚和新西兰。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 07:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-top-diplomat-visit-australia-new-zealand-says-foreign-minsitry-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于美联储宽松政策存在不确定性，中国央行周五将维持关键利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-set-leave-key-rate-unchanged-friday-amid-uncertainty-around-fed-2024-03-14/</link><description>路透调查显示，由于美联储降息时间存在不确定性，预计中国央行周五展期到期中期贷款时将维持关键政策利率不变。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 06:30:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-set-leave-key-rate-unchanged-friday-amid-uncertainty-around-fed-2024-03-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>